{"search_data": "Madhya PradeshMukhyamantri Bhavantar Bhugtan Yojana in MP to be Launched Soon \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Objectives of Mukhyamantri Bhavantar Bhugtan YojanaThe main objective of the scheme is to provide financial help to the farmers and bringing down the suicide rate eventually to zero in coming times. Apart from the financial help, the Mukhyamantri Bhavantar Bhugtan Yojana also aims to provide help to the farmers for several cases of disputes and ensure that all the cases are addressed within 90 days of first reporting.The government through the scheme also aims to encourage the farmers to produce certain pulses, oilseed and horticulture crops in their fields.Mukhyamantri Bhavantar Bhugtan Yojana \u2013 HighlightsBelow are the main highlights of the schemeThe scheme will ensure that farmers get the beneficial value of their product.The difference between the support price and the price of sale (at mandis) will be deposited directly into farmers\u2019 bank accounts by the state government.The crop Girdavari mobile app will compile the data regarding the farmers and their produces.The remunerative prices of crop will be suggested by the Madhya Pradesh Krishi Utpad Lagat and Vipanan Aayog.The scheme will ensure that the cases like partition, demarcation of land and the undisputed cases related to mutation to be addressed within three months.However, if the farmers claims that after three month their case is still pending despite it being undisputed, the government will give reward to that farmer and the amount of reward will be deducted from the concerned employee and punitive action also will be taken against the employee of the department.In Madhya Pradesh, agriculture sector leads in the production of farm product like grain, linseed, green pea etc. The state govt. is also expanding areas under cultivation of safflower and sunflower. It becomes imperative to provide sufficient space for vitality of farmers for yielding production by state government.Mukhyamantri Bhavantar Bhugtan Yojana is not launched yet, the scheme contours are still being finalized, once the scheme is launched, all the details would be updated here.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}